    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276612</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_160_020_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>追おう！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Get him!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276676</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_160_020_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>行かないの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're not going with them?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276764</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_160_020_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレ、
どうしていいか
わかんね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why...Why is this happening? I don't get it...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276876</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_160_020_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>バジルさんがどうして、
こんなことしてるか、
気にならないの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Don't you want to know why
Mister Basil came all the way
here? Why he's doing this?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276988</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_160_020_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>バジル……そうか、
あの人は人工マナの開発者、
バジル博士か</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Basil... That's right! Professor Basil,
he was the head researcher behind
the development of artificial mana!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277084</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_160_020_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>人工マナ？
バジルさんが
そんなことを……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Artificial mana? Mister Basil
was working on that...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277296</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_160_020_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>博士は長い時間をかけ、魔科学に
代わる力を研究していました。
それが人工マナです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The Professor has spent much of
his time developing an energy
source to replace Magitechnology.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277296</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_160_020_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも……そのバジル博士が、
どうして『シグルド』の
指導者に？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But...why would Professor Basil
be the leader of a criminal 
organization like Sigurd?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277384</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_160_020_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>本人に聞いた方が
早いかもしれないな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We won't know until we
hear it from Basil himself.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277468</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_160_020_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ……&lt;Dio&gt;を
追いかけようぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah...Let's go catch up to &lt;Dio&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
